Ally Invest requires a minimum opening purchase order of $100.00 per order in OTCBB and Pink Sheet stocks and adds 1 cent per share on the entire order for stocks priced less than $2.00.  Maximum commission per order not to exceed 5% of the trade value, with minimum commission of $4.95. Ally does not accept opening trades for stocks below 1 cent per share. Commissions and fees from published web sites as of 4/11/2017. Some brokers may offer more competitive fees than the ones published if certain balances or levels of activity are met. Please contact each broker individually to confirm their commission schedule. See our fees.



