Stocks are the most common type of security and represent ownership in an organization. When you purchase a stock share, you're anticipating the value of that stock will increase. There are thousands of stocks to choose from and multiple
                  ways to invest in stocks.







Trade for just $ plus 65 cents per contract
                    

